Enough has been said about Bombay’s charm, but for creatives like Maia, the city’s magic lies in its nuances. ✨ For the founder of Papaaya Swimwear, it’s a city of endless inspiration, but more importantly, a place called home – from the punchy flavors of Ayyub’s chicken tikka roll to the freedom of hopping into a kaali-peeli. Join her on a tour of her Bombay, where work, style, and identity blend seamlessly. Accessorised in our Villa Isharya & I For Isharya collections, she shares her favorite haunts, model off-duty aesthetic, and what makes this city truly hers. 🏡❤️‍🔥
